<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Activation Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.875rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #014142;
    }

    .email-button {
      padding: 12px 20px;
      margin: 8px 0;
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 4px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      color: white;
      background: rgb(34,193,195);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Parlons - Instant Messaging Web App</h1>
  <p>Hello <b>{{name}}</b>! </p>
  <p>If you have forgotten your password, you can reset it by clicking on the button below. Please note that the link will expire after 30 minutes. </p>
  <a class="email-button" href={{link}} target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
  <p>Or paste this link into your browser:</p>
  <a href={{link}} target="_blank">{{link}}</a>
  <p> If you did not request this information, please ignore this email or contact customer service.</p>
</body>
</html>